WEBVTT

00:02.789 --> 00:05.358
- I know when I've had enough.
- So do I.

00:06.289 --> 00:08.672
The bomb went off
when she opened the door.

00:08.758 --> 00:11.154
The victim is indeed
Olivia Walsh.

00:11.239 --> 00:13.194
This morning,
when I saw that blast scene,

00:13.279 --> 00:15.174
it all came back
like it was yesterday.

00:15.259 --> 00:16.273
Orla.

00:16.359 --> 00:18.184
If I'm to go opening up
doors again,

00:18.269 --> 00:20.359
I need a better reason
than a favour to an old mate.

00:20.492 --> 00:23.154
I've driven Mr Lawson to a number
of meetings recently.

00:23.239 --> 00:25.204
If the killings start,
there's nothing you can do about it.

00:25.289 --> 00:27.229
Just leave it alone.

00:28.739 --> 00:31.398
- We have to do this together.
- Do what?

00:31.492 --> 00:34.204
She's met your mother.
Now, she deserves justice.

00:34.289 --> 00:35.969
- Mr Alex Harris?
- Hi.

00:36.055 --> 00:37.539
Do you know this woman?

00:37.625 --> 00:39.948
Olivia initiated
the affair,

00:40.034 --> 00:41.875
but she didn't seem
to enjoy it very much.

00:41.961 --> 00:44.866
Pat Walsh sprays the blood
all over his walls.

00:44.961 --> 00:46.492
Staged his own death.

00:46.578 --> 00:48.039
Niall Malloy.

00:48.125 --> 00:52.515
Joined the IRA in '76. Earned him
his nickname, Death Maker.

00:52.601 --> 00:54.750
- Does he know who did this to Mum?
- Maybe.

00:55.002 --> 00:56.164
I didn't talk.

00:56.766 --> 00:58.799
Niall, I'm begging you!

01:00.069 --> 01:01.219
Please.

01:01.305 --> 01:08.312
<i>♪ Testator silens ♪</i>

01:10.351 --> 01:17.750
<i>♪ Costestes e spiritu ♪</i>

01:17.851 --> 01:24.093
